briefdescription.para: Check the passed in persistentId if it is zero generate a new one. If it is non zero check it does not already exist on a part. If it Does exist, generate a new one and call GameEvent onPartpersistentIdChanged If removeOldId is true will remove old entry if a new one is generated. If addNewId is true will add new entry if a new one is generated. Finally it will add the persistentId if it wasn't found.
